This is the README for the FiRa Script Generation Tool / fira-sgt
###################################################################
1. Intro

The fira-sgt is a tool that allows to perform several FiRa applet 
related tasks without requiring in depth knowledge of the implementation.
The tool provides:
- injection of test keys into the FiRa applet, for development purposes
- generation of SCP11c secure scripts to create and provision ADFs

###################################################################
2. Preconditions
The tool requires JCShell and the FiRa applet must be installed.

###################################################################
3. Applet provisioning
If the applet is not provisioned (e.g. applet was sideloaded or 
updated from an older development version), the script 
fira-provision shall be executed in order to inject test keys.

If provisioning had already been done, the script fira-read-applet-cert
can be used to retrieve the applet SCP11c certificate.

